snippet.title: Sonic Fan Game - Sonic Time Twisted - SAGE 2014 Act 1 Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Download Demo: http://www.indiedb.com/games/sonic-time-twisted/downloads/sonic-time-twisted-sage-2014-act-1-demo

http://timetwisted.sonicstrike.net/


This SAGE, play the all-new, never-before-seen demo of Sonic Time Twisted, a classic-style Sonic fangame epic with time travel, accurate physics, custom pixel art, a fully original CD-quality soundtrack, and sprawling zones with loops, gizmos, alternate routes, and hidden secrets!

Trailer edited by Zach Hinchy. http://hinchy.us/





New Pixel Art and Spriting videos on Saturdays!
